{"version":1,"ops":[{"type":3,"author":{"id":"21d09849fb57b65fe65c91dbd8328cade69ab37e"},"timestamp":1618158755,"metadata":{"github-id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDgxNzMzNDU2OQ==","github-url":"https://github.com/rurban/smhasher/issues/190#issuecomment-817334569"},"message":"\u003e nmhash.h:490 -Wshift-count-overflow\n\nshould fix all warning now.","files":null},{"type":6,"author":{"id":"21d09849fb57b65fe65c91dbd8328cade69ab37e"},"timestamp":1618158755,"metadata":{"github-id":"MDE1OlVzZXJDb250ZW50RWRpdElzc3VlQ29tbWVudEVkaXQ6NDUwNzk1ODE3"},"target":"468446105d1a289165178e12f823585a38fdefa5c74f13632881edec5df43aa6","message":"\u003e nmhash.h:490 -Wshift-count-overflow\n\nshould fix all warning now, and do not need '/std:c++latest' for msvc","files":null},{"type":3,"author":{"id":"02a1aba681ab0b039dd509d683ddfb248d3ca047"},"timestamp":1618159866,"metadata":{"github-id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDgxNzMzNjM2MQ==","github-url":"https://github.com/rurban/smhasher/issues/190#issuecomment-817336361"},"message":"My qualification:\n\nExcellent quality and due to the SSE2/AVX2 optimizations very fast for large keys. But due to being 32bit only, it's mostly usable for hash tables, and there the most important short key speed lacks, because it's too much code. It's half as slow as the best, xxh3 and wyhash.","files":null},{"type":6,"author":{"id":"02a1aba681ab0b039dd509d683ddfb248d3ca047"},"timestamp":1618159866,"metadata":{"github-id":"MDE1OlVzZXJDb250ZW50RWRpdElzc3VlQ29tbWVudEVkaXQ6NDUwNzk3MTgy"},"target":"7074a4433330f47f9bb7063a66af78902c2db0171978c19d4ce44fe7663fec76","message":"My qualification:\n\nExcellent quality and due to the SSE2/AVX2 optimizations very fast for large keys. But due to being 32bit only, it's mostly usable for hash tables, and there the most important short key speed lacks, because it's too much code. It's half as slow as the best, xxh3 and wyhash.\n\nOn 32bit len \u003e\u003e 32 throws -Wshift-count-overflow","files":null},{"type":6,"author":{"id":"02a1aba681ab